                <h1>Ben & Jerry's: The Story Behind the Scoop</h1>
                <p>Ben & Jerry's was founded in 1978 by childhood friends Ben Cohen and Jerry Greenfield in Burlington, Vermont. Starting as a small ice cream parlor, they grew the brand into a global phenomenon renowned for its quirky flavors and commitment to social activism, using high-quality, sustainable ingredients while advocating for various causes.</p>
